text: Brittany Curran (born June 2, 1990) is an American actress. She played a "Six Chick" in 13 Going on 30. She also played Lucy Tranelli in Men of a Certain Age. She was born in Weymouth, Massachusetts. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Singers from Boston Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American child actors Category:Actors from Boston
